## Traps (carried forward)

- `pytest --timeout-method=signal` hangs on asyncio selector loops;
  use `--timeout-method=thread`.
- Pre-commit hook `pytest-check` fails in isolated worktrees.
  Use `git -c core.hooksPath=/dev/null commit` per `rules/git.md`.
- SQLite `UpdateNode` / `UpsertNode` return metadata only (not the
  row). PostgreSQL returns the row via RETURNING. Read-back via
  `self.read()` is the dialect-portable pattern ‚Äî established by
  #490 fix in `features/express.py`.
- Worktree dispatches silently base on old commits. Before cherry-
  picking any `worktree-agent-*` branch, check `git merge-base
  <branch> main`.

